{"tid":1140970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[倚天屠龍記] 空難聯今季會歌 - 得失一笑中","createTime":"2019-05-06T07:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T12:56:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84d58ac907847645b4ff04515b4b1201d8fe5984","tid":1140970,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:26:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ypAx668y7Z4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DypAx668y7Z4&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=f2dc8642\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ypAx668y7Z4</a><br />\n<br />\n作詞：王騎    作曲：張家誠<br />\n編曲：張家誠<br />\n監製：何哲圖 / 韋景雲<br />\n<br />\n傳聞獌聯動 劃破蘇B這天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普巴風捲起 變暗湧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾扮無敵 難逃避命運擺弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六弟 破解心底怨萬重</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盧卡~ 古~ 光照見迷夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獌狗 千百種 糾結半生 未揭盅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回望這個費爵殺敵無數 被英超作弄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每隻廢獌如像看通 又狂傲似瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成就世界最大縱被狂串 得失恥笑中</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誰伴我 攀不上巔峰 甘於兩袖清風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6900de52e1d5cf05e0befbf2cd2889a6406d6b71","tid":1140970,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"歡迎轉貼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6746a48fdac95f131e5df605221e90c0cdf27521","tid":1140970,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5d0f5de755b1f4c982908d9dc1b2419a6410f583","tid":1140970,"uid":3028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"猁伴我 攀不上巔峰 甘於四大皆空"},{"pid":"173d244b231339436d35eb5a5170e80727f8d6b4","tid":1140970,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0f5de755b1f4c982908d9dc1b2419a6410f583","tid":1140970,"uid":3028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"猁伴我 攀不上巔峰 甘於四大皆空"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\